name: CONQUER.WAD
description: Twisty passageways and sniper nests surroud A large open pentagram shaped chamber. The only weapons you'll find are the shotgun, chaingun, and Rocket Launcher (Great fun in the sniper nests - Be careful though, some of the 'nests' can suddenly become not-so-secret!). Anyone can get a frag with the Plasma gun, so weenies keep out. ;-)
